<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>La Classe 1F si racconta</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,400;0,9..144,700;0,9..144,900;1,9..144,400&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #FEF6EC;
    --orange: #E05C2B;
    --orange-light: #F4936A;
    --teal: #0D7377;
    --teal-light: #14A098;
    --yellow: #F2C94C;
    --yellow-light: #FDE58A;
    --rose: #D64E6A;
    --dark: #1D2535;
    --mid: #3D4B5C;
    --light-text: #6B7A8E;
    --card-bg: #ffffff;
    --border: #E8DECE;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--dark);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .hero {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: white;
    padding: 70px 40px 60px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; right: -80px;
    width: 340px; height: 340px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--orange);
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -60px; left: -60px;
    width: 260px; height: 260px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--teal);
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  .hero-inner { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--orange);
    color: white;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 7vw, 68px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero h1 span { color: var(--yellow); }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .hero-dates {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  }

  .hero-dot { color: var(--orange-light); font-size: 22px; line-height: 1; }

  .hero-stat-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-stat {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
  }

  .hero-stat .num {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--yellow);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-stat .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
  .section {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--orange);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-tag::before {
    content: '';
    width: 20px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--orange);
    display: block;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--light-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* ===== DIVIDER ===== */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ===== WORD CLOUD ===== */
  .word-cloud-bg {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  .word-cloud-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .word-cloud-inner .section-tag { color: var(--yellow); }
  .word-cloud-inner .section-tag::before { background: var(--yellow); }
  .word-cloud-inner h2 { color: white; }
  .word-cloud-inner .subtitle { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

  .word-cloud {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .word {
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .word:hover { transform: scale(1.07); }
  .word.xl { font-size: 48px; padding: 8px 16px; background: var(--orange); color: white; }
  .word.lg { font-size: 34px; padding: 6px 14px; background: var(--teal); color: white; }
  .word.md { font-size: 24px; padding: 5px 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: white; }
  .word.sm { font-size: 17px; padding: 4px 10px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }

  .word-note {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ===== COMPARISON BLOCKS ===== */
  .compare-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .compare-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .compare-card {
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .compare-card.inizio { background: #FFF8F2; border-color: #F0D9C5; }
  .compare-card.fine { background: #F2FAFB; border-color: #C5E2E4; }

  .compare-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .compare-label.inizio { color: var(--orange); }
  .compare-label.fine { color: var(--teal); }

  .compare-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .compare-dot.inizio { background: var(--orange); }
  .compare-dot.fine { background: var(--teal); }

  /* ===== MATERIE CHART ===== */
  .materie-section {
    background: white;
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  .materie-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .materie-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .tab-btn {
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    background: white;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    color: var(--mid);
  }

  .tab-btn.active.migliori {
    background: var(--teal);
    border-color: var(--teal);
    color: white;
  }

  .tab-btn.active.peggiori {
    background: var(--rose);
    border-color: var(--rose);
    color: white;
  }

  .chart-panel { display: none; }
  .chart-panel.active { display: block; }

  .chart-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .chart-col {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 240px;
  }

  .chart-col-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  .bar-item {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .bar-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .bar-name {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .bar-count {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--light-text);
    background: #f3f4f6;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1px 7px;
  }

  .bar-track {
    height: 8px;
    background: #F0F0F0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: width 1s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .bar-fill.teal { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal), var(--teal-light)); }
  .bar-fill.rose { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--rose), #E97A93); }
  .bar-fill.orange { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), var(--orange-light)); }

  /* ===== STUDIO SECTION ===== */
  .strategies-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(190px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .strategy-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .strategy-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .strategy-icon {
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .strategy-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .strategy-bar-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .strategy-mini-bar {
    flex: 1;
    height: 5px;
    background: #F0F0F0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .strategy-mini-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .strategy-note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--light-text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .strategy-num {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ===== AIUTI / DISTRAZIONI ===== */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .bubble-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .bubble-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--mid);
  }

  .bubble-icon { flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 1px; }

  .ad-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ad-label.aiuto { background: #E8F8F4; color: var(--teal); }
  .ad-label.ostacolo { background: #FFF0F0; color: var(--rose); }

  /* ===== SOGNI ===== */
  .dreams-bg {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D2535 0%, #0D3B4C 100%);
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  .dreams-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .dreams-inner .section-tag { color: var(--yellow); }
  .dreams-inner .section-tag::before { background: var(--yellow); }
  .dreams-inner h2 { color: white; }
  .dreams-inner .subtitle { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

  .dreams-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .dream-pill {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .dream-pill:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
  .dream-pill.l { font-size: 17px; padding: 12px 22px; }
  .dream-pill.xl { font-size: 20px; padding: 14px 26px; font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; }

  .dream-pill.orange { background: var(--orange); color: white; }
  .dream-pill.teal { background: var(--teal); color: white; }
  .dream-pill.yellow { background: var(--yellow); color: var(--dark); }
  .dream-pill.rose { background: var(--rose); color: white; }
  .dream-pill.muted { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }

  /* ===== QUOTE CARDS ===== */
  .quotes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .quote-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .quote-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }

  .quote-card::before {
    content: '\201C';
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 60px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--orange-light);
    opacity: 0.4;
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 16px;
  }

  .quote-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--mid);
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .quote-card p em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .quote-meta {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--light-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ===== CRESCITA ===== */
  .crescita-bg {
    background: white;
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  .crescita-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .growth-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 60px 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .growth-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 5px;
    }
    .arrow-col { display: none; }
  }

  .growth-cell {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--mid);
  }

  .growth-cell.before { border-left: 3px solid var(--orange); }
  .growth-cell.after { border-left: 3px solid var(--teal); }

  .arrow-col {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--light-text);
  }

  /* ===== GRUPPO ===== */
  .gruppo-bg {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F2FAF8 0%, var(--cream) 100%);
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  .gruppo-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .gruppo-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(230px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .gruppo-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 22px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .gruppo-card .g-icon {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .gruppo-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .gruppo-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--light-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
  .footer-section {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 24px;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .footer-section span { color: var(--orange-light); }

  /* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .fade-up { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards; }

  .bar-fill { width: 0; }
  .bars-animated .bar-fill { animation: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner fade-up">
    <div class="hero-tag">Tirocinio · Sostegno Scuola Media</div>
    <h1>La Classe <span>1F</span><br>si racconta</h1>
    <p>Due questionari, un anno scolastico. Voci, pensieri e trasformazioni di ragazze e ragazzi della classe prima della scuola secondaria di primo grado, raccolti all'inizio e alla fine del tirocinio.</p>
    <div class="hero-dates">
      <span>Novembre 2024</span>
      <span class="hero-dot">→</span>
      <span>Aprile 2025</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== WORD CLOUD ===== -->
<section class="word-cloud-bg">
  <div class="word-cloud-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">Fine anno · A fine aprile</div>
    <h2>L'anno in tre parole</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Abbiamo chiesto ai ragazzi di descrivere il loro anno scolastico in massimo tre parole. Ecco cosa hanno risposto.</p>

    <div class="word-cloud">
      <span class="word xl">divertente</span>
      <span class="word lg">bello</span>
      <span class="word lg">impegnativo</span>
      <span class="word md">nuovo</span>
      <span class="word md">interessante</span>
      <span class="word sm">faticoso</span>
      <span class="word sm">strano</span>
      <span class="word sm">collaborativo</span>
      <span class="word sm">amicizia</span>
      <span class="word sm">veloce</span>
      <span class="word sm">difficile</span>
      <span class="word sm">studioso</span>
      <span class="word sm">lunghissimo</span>
    </div>

    <p class="word-note">La dimensione delle parole è proporzionale al numero di volte che sono state usate dai ragazzi.</p>

    <div class="compare-grid" style="margin-top: 40px;">
      <div class="compare-card inizio">
        <div class="compare-label inizio"><span class="compare-dot inizio"></span>Inizio anno · Novembre</div>
        <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--mid);">
          All'inizio molti ragazzi descrivono l'avvio dell'anno come <strong>"bello"</strong> e <strong>"divertente"</strong>, ma anche con una punta di ansia o agitazione. Alcuni erano <em>curiosi</em>, altri <em>un po' emozionati</em> per i nuovi insegnanti e la nuova classe.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="compare-card fine">
        <div class="compare-label fine"><span class="compare-dot fine"></span>Fine anno · Aprile</div>
        <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--mid);">
          A fine anno il tono cambia: l'anno è ancora <strong>"divertente"</strong> e <strong>"bello"</strong>, ma ora emerge anche <strong>"impegnativo"</strong> — segno di una consapevolezza cresciuta del percorso scolastico.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== RELAZIONI ===== -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-tag">Vita di classe</div>
  <h2>Come mi trovo con i compagni?</h2>
  <p class="subtitle">Una delle domande più significative riguardava le relazioni con i compagni di classe, sia a inizio che a fine anno.</p>

  <div class="compare-grid">
    <div class="compare-card inizio">
      <div class="compare-label inizio"><span class="compare-dot inizio"></span>Inizio anno</div>
      <div class="bubble-list">
        <div class="bubble-item"><span class="bubble-icon">😊</span> La maggior parte si trova bene, ma le amicizie sono ancora in costruzione</div>
        <div class="bubble-item"><span class="bubble-icon">🤝</span> Molti avevano amici già dalle elementari o dalla classe precedente</div>
        <div class="bubble-item"><span class="bubble-icon">🌱</span> Alcune ragazze iniziano a stringere nuove amicizie all'interno della classe</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="compare-card fine">
      <div class="compare-label fine"><span class="compare-dot fine"></span>Fine anno</div>
      <div class="bubble-list">
        <div class="bubble-item"><span class="bubble-icon">💚</span> Quasi tutti riferiscono di trovarsi bene, spesso con più amici di prima</div>
        <div class="bubble-item"><span class="bubble-icon">🔄</span> Il cambio di posto ha favorito nuove amicizie inaspettate</div>
        <div class="bubble-item"><span class="bubble-icon">🌟</span> Molti descrivono la classe come "più unita" rispetto a settembre</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ===== MATERIE ===== -->
<section class="materie-section">
  <div class="materie-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">Apprendimento</div>
    <h2>Le materie preferite e le più difficili</h2>
